<title>km ạ̉nt ly</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- km ạ̉nt ly mḥb rby wmạ ạ̉smạk
 ḥbk fạq dwmạaⁿ mdạy wạlạ̹drạk
 kyf ạ̹tkẖdẖtny ạ̹bnạaⁿ ạ̉gẖly̱ mn ạlạ̉mlạk
 wwạrtẖạaⁿ lmjd ạ̉ʿly̱ mn ạlạ̉flạk
 2- km bạṭạ zmạny tḥt ạlsmạ lwlạk
 kẖlf ạlsrạb yqḍy fy ạlkd wạlạ̹nhạk
 km lys fyh mʿny̱ mhmạ ḥlạ ạ̉w sẖạk
 ḥty̱ tḥl fyh bạlfyḍ mn nʿmạk
 3- tmḍy kdẖạ ạlsnyn wạlḥb ybqy̱ dẖạk
 ʿyny ạ̹lyk trnw flys ly ạ̹lạk
 ạ̉lqạk kl fjr wạ̉sẖthy rw̉yạk
 ḥty̱ yjỷ fjr ʿyny bh tlqạk</lyrics>
</song>